info.description:
Complete API endpoints for Laravel E-commerce including Products, Orders, Categories, Attributes, Banners, Brands, Bundles, Carts, Complaints, Coupons, Front (Home, Products, Blog, Search, Recommendations), Google2FA, Messages, Newsletters, OpenAI, Pages, Permissions, Posts, Product Stats, Product Tracking, Roles, Settings (General, Email, Payment, Shipping, SEO), Shipping Methods and Calculation, Tags, Tenants, Users, Wishlist, Admin Analytics, System, Translations, Reviews, Import/Export, and Comparison. Updated with all new endpoints.

Base URL: {{base_url}}

All endpoints require Bearer token authentication except Product Comparison, Front endpoints, Product Tracking endpoints, and Wishlist endpoints which work with or without authentication.

